1080
01:20:30,541 --> 01:20:32,791
Kisah pembunuh bersiri.

1081
01:20:33,875 --> 01:20:35,415
Dia kata itu babak cinta.

1082
01:20:35,416 --> 01:20:36,500
Cinta?

1083
01:20:37,750 --> 01:20:40,125
