Gadis itu cintakan dia?

1086
01:20:46,375 --> 01:20:47,708
Itu yang dia cakap.

1087
01:20:48,916 --> 01:20:50,000
Dia ada sebut nama?

1088
01:20:52,541 --> 01:20:55,125
Kir... Keerthana?

1089
01:20:56,375 --> 01:20:57,458
Krithika.

1090
01:20:58,291 --> 01:20:59,291
Krithika?

1091
01:21:02,416 --> 01:21:05,375
Apa babak dia suruh awak lakonkan?
Boleh terangkan?

1092
01:21:15,416 --> 01:21:17,166
Awak pernah jatuh cinta?

1093
01:21:23,000 --> 01:21:24,125
Jadi, siapa Krithika?

1094
01:21:32,583 --> 01:21:33,666
Michael.

1095
01:22:48,291 --> 01:22:50,999
<i>Hei, si gadis, kaulah</i>

1096
01:22:51,000 --> 01:22:53,915
<i>Magnet yang menarikku</i>

1097
01:22:53,916 --> 01:22:57,125
<i>Mata yang melangkaui jiwa</i>

1098
01:23:00,166 --> 01:23:03,207
<i>Senyumanmu yang bersinar</i>

1099
01:23:03,208 --> 01:23:06,165
<i>Memukauku</i>

1100
01:23:06,166 --> 01:23:07,499
