01:46:59,000 --> 01:47:00,582
Saya jatuhkan hukuman

1366
01:47:00,583 --> 01:47:03,458
penjara seumur hidup
ke atas tertuduh, Stephen.

1367
01:47:05,041 --> 01:47:08,207
Pentadbiran penjara
perlu pantau kesihatan mentalnya

1368
01:47:08,208 --> 01:47:12,791
dan membimbingnya dengan baik.

1369
01:47:16,208 --> 01:47:17,333
Mahkamah bersurai.

1370
01:47:41,750 --> 01:47:42,958
HENTIKAN KEKERASAN TERHADAP WANITA

1371
01:47:45,166 --> 01:47:46,499
KAMI NAK KEADILAN!

1372
01:47:46,500 --> 01:47:48,166
KEADILAN HAK ASASI KAMI

1373
01:47:50,416 --> 01:47:51,999
Tahan dia!

1374
01:47:52,000 --> 01:47:53,375
Beri laluan!

1375
01:47:54,041 --> 01:47:54,958
Beri laluan!

1376
01:47:55,875 --> 01:47:57,291
Berlindung.

1377
01:47:58,625 --> 01:47:59,708
Berlindung.

1378
01:48:01,458 --> 01:48:04,082
- Ke tepi.
- Masukkan dia dalam bas.

1379
01:48:04,083 --> 01:48:05,541
Masuk.

1380
01:48:11,750 --> 01:48:13,791
Hidupkan enjin. Bergerak. Jalan.

1381
01:48:17,416 --> 01:48:18,625
Jangan tanya apa-apa.

1382
01:48:20,125 --> 01:48:21,999
Jangan tanya apa-apa, puan.

1383
01:48:22,000 --> 01:48:25,416
Kami tak boleh komen. Kes ditutup.

1384
01:48:26,875 --> 01:48:27,916
Tiada komen.

1385
01:48:28,708 --> 01:48:30,165
Mahkamah dah buat keputusan.

1386
01:48:30,166 --> 01:48:31,790
Kami tak boleh buat apa-apa.

1387
01:48:31,791 --> 01:48:32,875
Dah selesai.

1388
01:48:46,583 --> 01:48:51,249
{\an8}TAMAT
SALAM IKHLAS, STEPHEN

1389
01:48:51,250 --> 01:48:53,041
{\an8}<i>Hei, sudahlah.</i>

1390
01:48:54,458 --> 01:48:55,458
{\an8}Hei, marilah.

1391
01:48:58,916 --> 01:49:00,041
Bagus tak?

1392
01:49:12,291 --> 01:49:13,375
Stephen.

1393
01:49:14,708 --> 01:49:16,208
Kamu bunuh Kuttan, bukan?

1394
01:49:20,291 --> 01:49:22,041
Beritahu hal sebenar.

1395
01:49:22,833 --> 01:49:24,958
Ayah tak bunuh Kuttan. Mengakulah!

1396
01:49:33,083 --> 01:49:35,833
<i>Saya tiba-tiba terdorong
untuk membunuhnya.</i>

1397
01:49:36,958 --> 01:49:39,000
Ayah buat dua kesilapan besar.

1398
01:49:40,958 --> 01:49:43,791
Jadi pemabuk
kerana gagal jadi pemain hebat.

1399
01:49:44,666 --> 01:49:45,625
Kedua...

1400
01:49:46,250 --> 01:49:47,791
sayang kamu sepenuh hati.

1401
01:49:58,708 --> 01:50:01,250
Kamu letak kamera
di bilik persalinan pelajar, bukan?

1402
01:50:04,250 --> 01:50:05,250
<i>Betul.</i>

1403
01:50:07,416 --> 01:50:09,750
<i>Ayah sanggup tanggung kesalahan itu.</i>

1404
01:50:10,458 --> 01:50:11,791
<i>Tapi nak tahu?</i>

1405
01:50:12,791 --> 01:50:15,166
<i>Apabila dewasa,
saya hilang minat pada wanita.</i>

1406
01:50:15,875 --> 01:50:17,875
<i>Saya hanya fokus membunuh.</i>

1407
01:50:19,750 --> 01:50:22,416
<i>Kamu bunuh kucing dan anjing
untuk suka-suka.</i>

1408
01:50:22,916 --> 01:50:24,750
<i>Kemudian, manusia.</i>

1409
01:50:26,083 --> 01:50:29,916
<i>Mengaku kamu yang tikam mak kamu
kerana tak benarkan kamu kerja.</i>

1410
01:50:37,125 --> 01:50:42,166
<i>Beritahu mereka yang kamu ugut ayah kamu
supaya serah diri dan kelar lehernya.</i>

1411
01:50:46,500 --> 01:50:47,625
Kenapa bunuh kami?

1412
01:50:49,083 --> 01:50:50,333
Apa dosa kami?

1413
01:50:52,166 --> 01:50:53,416
Cakaplah, celaka!

1414
01:50:54,250 --> 01:50:56,291
Hei! Siapa yang cakap tadi?

1415
01:50:59,166 --> 01:51:01,082
- Sebut.
- Celaka.

1416
01:51:01,083 --> 01:51:02,040
Bukan awak.

1417
01:51:02,041 --> 01:51:03,249
- Sebut.
- Celaka.

1418
01:51:03,250 --> 01:51:05,708
- Tak. Awak?
- Celaka.

1419
01:51:06,375 --> 01:51:07,208
Dapat pun!

1420
01:51:09,333 --> 01:51:10,916
Saya tak ingat pun nama awak.

1421
01:51:11,458 --> 01:51:13,500
Berani awak sertai mereka dan maki saya?

1422
01:51:14,375 --> 01:51:15,625
Siaplah awak.

1423
01:51:19,375 --> 01:51:21,791
Keluarga siapa yang meracuni saya?

1424
01:51:23,458 --> 01:51:25,125
Dalam kopi kesukaan saya pula.

1425
01:51:25,958 --> 01:51:29,416
Cakaplah, bodoh.

1426
01:51:31,333 --> 01:51:33,416
Kamu nak tahu kenapa kamu dibunuh, bukan?

1427
01:51:34,041 --> 01:51:35,750
Barulah roh kamu tenang.

1428
01:51:36,875 --> 01:51:38,624
Kadangkala saya rindu Krithika.

1429
01:51:38,625 --> 01:51:42,165
<i>Jadi saya suruh kamu berlakon menjadi dia
dan bunuh kamu.</i>

1430
01:51:42,166 --> 01:51:44,374
<i>Saya layan kamu dengan sopan!</i>

1431
01:51:44,375 --> 01:51:45,750
<i>Pernahkah saya biadab?</i>

1432
01:51:46,333 --> 01:51:48,082
Membunuh beri saya keseronokan.

1433
01:51:48,083 --> 01:51:50,625
Selain itu, saya tak berminat. Faham?

1434
01:51:51,416 --> 01:51:53,291
Kamu tak penting dalam hidup saya.

1435
01:51:56,000 --> 01:51:58,416
Saya nak buat sepuluh tekan tubi.

1436
01:51:59,208 --> 01:52:04,583
Pastikan kamu semua hilang
sebelum saya selesai, okey?

1437
01:52:06,375 --> 01:52:07,375
Tolong faham.

1438
01:52:09,416 --> 01:52:10,541
Jangan buat saya marah.

1439
01:52:29,500 --> 01:52:31,416
Ayah? Bagaimana tubuh saya?

1440
01:52:33,000 --> 01:52:34,125
Cakaplah, ayah.

1441
01:52:37,541 --> 01:52:40,207
Mak, cakaplah.

1442
01:52:40,208 --> 01:52:41,625
Mak ada hak.

1443
01:52:45,583 --> 01:52:46,583
Sayang?

1444
01:52:47,291 --> 01:52:48,625
Dulu kita berbual lama.

1445
01:52:49,666 --> 01:52:51,750
Kenapa sekarang awak diam saja?

1446
01:52:52,416 --> 01:52:53,458
Cakaplah, sayang.

1447
01:52:54,958 --> 01:52:57,708
Tolong ke tepi. Ke tepi.

1448
01:52:59,000 --> 01:53:00,000
Lihatlah awak!

1449
01:53:03,541 --> 01:53:08,958
Saya pernah mengaku bunuh mereka.

1450
01:53:10,458 --> 01:53:11,665
<i>Tapi awak kata,</i>

1451
01:53:11,666 --> 01:53:15,124
<i>"Pergilah serah diri, Stephen.
Saya akan tunggu awak."</i>

1452
01:53:15,125 --> 01:53:16,041
Betulkah?

1453
01:53:16,875 --> 01:53:19,083
Saya tipu tentang ayah dan mak.

1454
01:53:19,708 --> 01:53:21,291
Tapi awak cuba tipu saya?

1455
01:53:22,208 --> 01:53:23,958
Kata awak akan setia menunggu?

1456
01:53:25,000 --> 01:53:27,416
Jadi, saya terpaksa bunuh awak.

1457
01:53:28,333 --> 01:53:29,915
Pergilah tanya orang lain.

1458
01:53:29,916 --> 01:53:31,540
Pasal kita dan cinta kita...

1459
01:53:31,541 --> 01:53:34,291
Saya gambarkan awak seperti bidadari.

1460
01:53:34,916 --> 01:53:36,707
Mungkin sekarang awak ada sayap.

1461
01:53:36,708 --> 01:53:40,458
Kami didik kamu dengan baik.
Kenapa jadi begini?

1462
01:53:42,083 --> 01:53:43,791
Didik saya dengan baik?

1463
01:53:45,791 --> 01:53:47,665
<i>Saya sering dipukul.</i>

1464
01:53:47,666 --> 01:53:49,499
<i>Kami pukul untuk mendidik.</i>

1465
01:53:49,500 --> 01:53:51,000
<i>Adakah itu membantu?</i>

1466
01:53:52,625 --> 01:53:54,750
Kamu asyik cari pasal dengan saya.

1467
01:53:55,416 --> 01:53:57,500
Memang menyakitkan hati.

1468
01:53:58,250 --> 01:54:01,041
Sebab itulah saya bunuh kamu berdua.

1469
01:54:02,791 --> 01:54:04,708
<i>Saya tak berniat bunuh ayah.</i>

1470
01:54:05,291 --> 01:54:07,749
<i>Tapi saya takut dia terlepas cakap.</i>

1471
01:54:07,750 --> 01:54:09,957
<i>Jadi saya kelar lehernya untuk jaga-jaga.</i>

1472
01:54:09,958 --> 01:54:13,957
<i>Jika saya tahu Moorthy akan datang,
saya takkan bunuh dia.</i>

1473
01:54:13,958 --> 01:54:15,000
<i>Maaf, ayah.</i>

1474
01:54:16,625 --> 01:54:20,165
Seseorang pasti akan bongkarkan
semua kebenaran tentang kamu.

1475
01:54:20,166 --> 01:54:21,125
Lihatlah nanti.

1476
01:54:22,083 --> 01:54:23,415
Siapa, mak?

1477
01:54:23,416 --> 01:54:24,957
Seema?

1478
01:54:24,958 --> 01:54:26,958
Atau Michael?

1479
01:54:29,750 --> 01:54:30,750
Kenapa, mak?

1480
01:54:31,291 --> 01:54:32,708
Semuanya dirancang.

1481
01:54:34,916 --> 01:54:37,583
<i>Sepatutnya polis akan tangkap saya
selepas bunuh Mary</i>

1482
01:54:38,125 --> 01:54:40,124
<i>dan mereka akan bunuh saya terus di situ.</i>

1483
01:54:40,125 --> 01:54:43,082
<i>Michael boleh saja
acu pistol di mulut saya.</i>

1484
01:54:43,083 --> 01:54:44,790
<i>Mereka orang "baik".</i>

1485
01:54:44,791 --> 01:54:47,375
<i>Sebab itu saya rancang nak menyerah diri.</i>

1486
01:54:47,958 --> 01:54:53,332
Kemudian saya jalani banyak ujian, lulus,
yakinkan Seema, fokuskan ke Krithika,

1487
01:54:53,333 --> 01:54:55,624
buat Michael sibuk, sebut nama Mary,

1488
01:54:55,625 --> 01:54:57,874
kelirukan mereka dan lain-lain...

1489
01:54:57,875 --> 01:54:59,000
Oh, Tuhan!

1490
01:54:59,916 --> 01:55:02,166
Terlalu banyak kerja.

1491
01:55:02,791 --> 01:55:04,083
Ada sesiapa mampu buat?

1492
01:55:04,583 --> 01:55:06,874
Beritahu saya. Kamu mampu buat?

1493
01:55:06,875 --> 01:55:09,790
Kamu tahu cara untuk mati.
Kamu tahu cara bertahan?

1494
01:55:09,791 --> 01:55:10,874
Kamu perlu tahu.

1495
01:55:10,875 --> 01:55:15,040
Belajar kawal emosi orang,
menipu, manipulasi dan bertahan.

1496
01:55:15,041 --> 01:55:16,540
Kamu perlu tahu semua itu!

1497
01:55:16,541 --> 01:55:18,999
Baru kamu boleh hadap dunia kejam ini.

1498
01:55:19,000 --> 01:55:22,208
Orang baik akhirnya akan jadi macam kamu.

1499
01:55:22,875 --> 01:55:25,374
Saya takut dengan keputusan hakim.

1500
01:55:25,375 --> 01:55:30,207
Saya cuba bertahan, tertanya-tanya
sama ada dia pilih untuk gantung saya.

1501
01:55:30,208 --> 01:55:32,583
<i>Mujurlah, saya hanya
dipenjara seumur hidup.</i>

1502
01:55:34,541 --> 01:55:36,500
Hidup dalam penjara tak mudah.

1503
01:55:37,250 --> 01:55:38,665
Dua puluh lapan tahun!

1504
01:55:38,666 --> 01:55:40,708
Ayah tunggu untuk cakap begitu?

1505
01:55:41,333 --> 01:55:42,625
Kenapa, ayah?

1506
01:55:43,416 --> 01:55:44,540
Tengoklah,

1507
01:55:44,541 --> 01:55:47,790
saya akan dibebaskan dalam sepuluh tahun,
jika berkelakuan baik.

1508
01:55:47,791 --> 01:55:49,415
Sekarang saya 25 tahun.

1509
01:55:49,416 --> 01:55:51,832
Selepas 10 tahun, saya 35 tahun.

1510
01:55:51,833 --> 01:55:53,415
Yang penting, saya masih hidup.

1511
01:55:53,416 --> 01:55:57,832
Mampukah kehidupan begitu beri awak
kebahagiaan dan ketenangan, Stephen?

1512
01:55:57,833 --> 01:56:00,916
Hidup begini buat awak bahagia
dan tenang, Krithika?

1513
01:56:01,791 --> 01:56:03,791
Awak masih senaif dulu.

1514
01:56:04,500 --> 01:56:06,458
Hei, ayah. Pergilah.

1515
01:56:07,250 --> 01:56:08,291
Kenapa tunggu?

1516
01:56:08,958 --> 01:56:10,540
Ingat bas akan terbalik?

1517
01:56:10,541 --> 01:56:12,790
Itu takkan berlaku. Pergilah.

1518
01:56:12,791 --> 01:56:16,540
Jangan lupa, saya perlu berkelakuan baik.

1519
01:56:16,541 --> 01:56:18,625
Jangan buat saya marah dalam penjara.

1520
01:56:19,583 --> 01:56:20,583
Krithika?

1521
01:56:22,041 --> 01:56:23,375
Awak akan tunggu saya?

1522
01:56:27,750 --> 01:56:29,957
Nak buat apa dengan jawapan awak?

1523
01:56:29,958 --> 01:56:32,500
Dah terlambat!

1524
01:56:34,000 --> 01:56:35,750
Pergi.

1525
01:56:43,875 --> 01:56:47,957
<i>Jika awak fikir saya gila, mungkin ya.</i>

1526
01:56:47,958 --> 01:56:50,290
GILA!

1527
01:56:50,291 --> 01:56:51,415
{\an8}<i>Jika saya jahat, mungkin ya.</i>

1528
01:56:51,416 --> 01:56:52,375
{\an8}JAHAT!

1529
01:56:55,458 --> 01:56:57,125
{\an8}<i>Tapi bagi saya, saya cuma...</i>

1530
01:56:58,166 --> 01:56:59,000
{\an8}<i>Stephen.</i>

1531
01:57:03,125 --> 01:57:07,291
<i>Tak kira berapa kali saya ulang,
itulah hakikatnya.</i>

1532
01:57:13,291 --> 01:57:15,916
<i>Saya memang pelik begini. Apa nak buat?</i>

1533
01:57:19,458 --> 01:57:20,749
<i>Jangan cuba di rumah!</i>

1534
01:57:20,750 --> 01:57:21,915
JANGAN CUBA DI RUMAH!

1535
01:57:21,916 --> 01:57:23,166
<i>Pembunuhan...</i>

1536
01:57:24,541 --> 01:57:26,000
<i>satu kesalahan.</i>

1537
01:58:07,875 --> 01:58:10,000
<i>Jangan beritahu sesiapa, okey?</i>

1538
01:58:27,541 --> 01:58:30,708
Saya masih tak faham
bagaimana dia hapuskan mayat.

1539
01:58:31,458 --> 01:58:33,416
Mungkin betul apa yang dia kata.

1540
01:58:34,583 --> 01:58:37,457
Mungkin dia tak tahu apa-apa
selain buang mayat di hutan itu.

1541
01:58:37,458 --> 01:58:39,666
Kami pantau hutan itu hingga kini.

1542
01:58:40,375 --> 01:58:43,707
Tiada tanda-tanda pelik,
haiwan liar pun tiada.

1543
01:58:43,708 --> 01:58:45,124
{\an8}LIMA MINGGU LALU

1544
01:58:45,125 --> 01:58:48,999
{\an8}<i>Dalam fasa kedua siasatan
kes pembunuhan bersiri wanita muda,</i>

1545
01:58:49,000 --> 01:58:52,374
<i>mengikut kenyataan
pembunuh bersiri, Stephen Jebaraj,</i>

1546
01:58:52,375 --> 01:58:56,249
<i>mayat-mayat tersebut telah dibuang
di Hutan Anaikadu</i>

1547
01:58:56,250 --> 01:58:58,957
<i>berhampiran Sathyamangalam
di Daerah Erode.</i>

1548
01:58:58,958 --> 01:59:03,499
<i>Inspektor Michael dan pasukannya bergegas
ke tempat kejadian semalam,</i>

1549
01:59:03,500 --> 01:59:07,790
<i>tapi tak menemui mayat walaupun
pencarian dijalankan dengan teliti.</i>

1550
01:59:07,791 --> 01:59:11,458
<i>Hanya beberapa perhiasan
dan bukti ditemui.</i>

1551
01:59:12,250 --> 01:59:16,249
<i>Ia milik mangsa, Surekha dan Preethi.</i>

1552
01:59:16,250 --> 01:59:21,165
<i>SP George mengarahkan orang awam dan media
supaya tak mendekati tempat kejadian.</i>

1553
01:59:21,166 --> 01:59:25,124
<i>Kesahihan kenyataan pembunuh itu,
Stephen, mula diragui.</i>

1554
01:59:25,125 --> 01:59:28,458
<i>Di mana sebenarnya
mayat-mayat yang hilang itu?</i>

1555
02:00:37,166 --> 02:00:47,415
LUNA
KEBANGKITAN MALAM

1556
02:00:47,416 --> 02:00:51,000
BERSAMBUNG...

1557
02:02:17,000 --> 02:02:22,000
Terjemahan sari kata oleh Miza Khamis

